Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Section 9 Science File --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}塔奇克马式的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做诱饵也不轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想放主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种口径的榴弹炮也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦～克～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克就该有坦克的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.78,0:24:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用主炮用什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.64,0:24:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.26,0:24:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力也不够
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.28,0:24:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.59,0:24:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.78,0:25:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀的坦克胜过任何优秀的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.05,0:25:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也得换更强的火力系统
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是装缓冲器的空间不足
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果提高耐压极限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.23,0:25:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减速系统也不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.93,0:25:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用精简炸药也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.48,0:25:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是用穿甲弹吧


